<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح ن ق:</span> <span class="c2">(الْحَنَقُ)</span> الْغَيْظُ، وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(حِنَاقٌ)</span> كَجَبَلٍ وَجِبَالٍ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(حَنِقَ)</span> عَلَيْهِ مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(حَنِقٌ)</span> أَيِ اغْتَاظَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>